Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.96,0:02:41.97,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an6\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(1210,110)}Floral Delusion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she's been living in our garden lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she lives there, as radiant and beautiful as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's supposed to be a famous cherry tree around these parts.{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll stop by and take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard there's a famous cherry tree around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that tree should be right down this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I come from the other side of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I traveled here to get medicine for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That so? Your mother must be very dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a renowned doctor living up ahead or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He lives next to the cherry tree you asked about, and he's known for medicine that can cure any pain.{I know "cure"  here seems counter-intuitive, but it's a pretty common saying, especially for someone not in the doctor field.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even blooming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be taking my leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Good luck getting that medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disturb you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that you make medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you also ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good health is the one thing I have going for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good to hear.{dun dun dunnnnn}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare the medicine for your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so you should stay the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This tree is ancient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks to be at least six or seven centuries old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no sign of it having bloomed yet this season, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it's withered from age and is no longer able to bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't even notice her.{length}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her beauty is so radiant that it gives me the chills.{how positively pulchritudinous}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's something odd about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Has this cherry tree not bloomed yet this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she blind and deaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to be from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want something with Saho?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. It's just that something bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you her husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm a relative, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but has she lost her sight and hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Almost entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be because she's ingested the foam exuded by this tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ginko, a mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This tree is inhabited by the foam-like Kodama, or "Tree Spirit" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Trees inhabited by Kodama generally live for a very long time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and also bloom spectacularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when an animal ingests Kodama,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it can lose one or more of its five senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if we could ask her and find out whether that's the case here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but we cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, come with me, Saho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You may get a chill if you're out here after dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a doctor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be some way you can look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My family has been but simple gardeners for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gardeners?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We are only capable of caring for plants and bringing out their beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This cherry tree here, for example, is {a strain that is }resilient against disease, but it bears very small flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you graft in branches from a tree{strain} that bears beautiful flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the resilient cherry tree will come to bear beautiful flowers as well{ instead of small ones}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,While my family studied plants in this manner,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we also began to create medicines from their flowers, \Nand share our results with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made medicine from the mushi-infested cherry tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That tree is a special tree that my family has protected for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We would never use it for such a purpose.{lol full o' shit.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where you get your famous painkilling medicine?{Good ol' Ginko, not trusting anyone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you that it only deadens one's senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're careful with how much you ingest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,your senses will eventually return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You experimented with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never do such a horrible thing!{lol sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My family has been researching plants for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course when we discovered that strange foam{ coming out of that cherry tree},
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we had to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Three or so of my ancestors \Ncould see the strange foam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of them studied it for years and devised a safe dosage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not the sap of a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The foam itself is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything bad were to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,would you be able to take countermeasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You must leave that behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are those who have need of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many who care not whether they can see or hear, so long as they can escape the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives you the right to take that choice away from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, first show me your family's research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will determine myself whether the findings are trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll show you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing. About that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If her condition is truly caused by the Kodama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we may be able to restore her sight and hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you {\i1}sure{\i0} you don't know how she became that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a story that has been passed down since my great-grandfather was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your great-grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A story from when he was a young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A story from nearly eighty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have abandoned a baby like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this faint pink foam on her mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it sap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have been so hungry \Nthat she sucked on the tree sap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My great-grandfather, Mansaku, took the infant home with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, his wife could not produce milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The infant even refused thin gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing she would drink was the tree sap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mansaku's family cared for the child \Nas though she were one of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But even after many years, the child hardly grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She remained an infant for over a decade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,still only willing to drink the sap of that cherry tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After thirty years, Mansaku and his wife passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but Saho remained but a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come, Saho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Mansaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Daddy Mansaku is no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now on, you'll be living with me, your big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho had almost completely lost use of all five senses, \Nincluding her sight and hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, she also fell ill periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,During the years when Saho was in poor health,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the giant cherry tree would not bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Subsequent generations continued to protect and cherish Saho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaki, you must...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You must take care of Saho...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us have loved Saho as though she were the very spirit of that cherry tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty years?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This means the Kodama bestows longevity and beauty to animals as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can Saho be cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is indeed a way to extract the Kodama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,if we remove the Kodama from her and try to restore her senses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho may not survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That is unfortunate, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all of my family's records on the foam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Saho?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared the medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd like you to try it for yourself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It is rare, but there are some who have poor reactions to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you react well to it, your mother should be fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some of these are very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many generations ago is this, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:55.05,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.3\c&H1B242C&\fscx82\fscy82\1a&HD0&\frz6.601\pos(973,308)\alpha&HD0&}Recorded by \N{\fs68}Mansaku
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.05,0:15:55.05,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fax-0.3\c&H1B242C&\fscx82\fscy82\1a&H8B&\frz6.601\pos(973,308)}Recorded by \N{\fs68}Mansaku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said Mansaku was his great-grandfather, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, these look...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:10.07,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(642,119)\frz21.11\c&H7E8A90&\alpha&H80&}M{*\c&H758187&}a{*\c&H6D787F&}s{*\c&H646E76&}a{*\c&H5C656E&}k{\c&H535C65&}i
