Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are four names scattered among the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean four successive generations were able to see mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is extremely rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.07,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.3\c&H1B242C&\1a&HD0&\frz6.601\fscx113\fscy113\pos(591,182)\alpha&HD0&}Recorded by \N{\fs68}Mansaku
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.07,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.3\c&H1B242C&\1a&HA6&\frz6.601\fscx113\fscy113\pos(591,182)}Recorded by \N{\fs68}Mansaku
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What I gave you just now was merely a sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to interference, I couldn't give you the painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to make this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to bloom once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been grafting whole bodies as you would tree branches—{length}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,all to keep her alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for a mere eighty years, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but for centuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mansaku was my ancestor from {\i1}eight{\i0} generations ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do not do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho's body will deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she is still so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,saku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you a new body right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how many lives have already been sacrificed for her to live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps there {\i1}is{\i0} something wrong with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For three hundred years, our family has loved a woman who is like a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!{Oh my god!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire! It's spreading to the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cherry blossoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho, look at the cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree has bloomed again—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is said that some ancient trees come to possess souls of their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and thus entice and enthrall the hearts of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is also said that should such a tree have a bloom that is beauteous and radiant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the effect is even more profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cherry tree avoided being burned to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, neither the gardener nor the woman were ever seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what beautiful cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they seem to melt away the weariness of travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to take a rest around here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wonderful idea. \NA perfect place to enjoy a small drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in no hurry, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But my, what a splendid sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's nothing quite like it.
